aan}, F.~H.</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2009-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:outcomeId>bib_17438_98db6fc509</gtr:outcomeId></gtr:publication><gtr:publication><gtr:id>EB6F4799-37F2-4D5F-BA5A-0DF6329A6570</gtr:id><gtr:title>Development of net-shape piezoelectric actuators for large x-ray optics</gtr:title><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.ukri.org:80/person/75bec35498500a699716db5e0a3fe2c3"><gtr:id>75bec35498500a699716db5e0a3fe2c3</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Rodriguez Sanmartin D</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2010-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:outcomeId>bib_17438_fbd5b69bf1</gtr:outcomeId></gtr:publication><gtr:publication><gtr:id>491996B2-72A9-46C8-9104-7FA175729791</gtr:id><gtr:title>An X-ray Polaroid filter for the IXO Narrow Field Imager</gtr:title><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.ukri.org:80/person/a7e5563b8998df26600635f95878f408"><gtr:id>a7e5563b8998df26600635f95878f408</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>{Bannister}, N. and {Martindale}, A. and {Willingale}, R. and {Fraser}, G.</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2009-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:outcomeId>bib_17438_5e78c18e68</gtr:outcomeId></gtr:publication><gtr:publication><gtr:id>55EFA9B4-06DF-4440-A213-9DB05097BD6C</gtr:id><gtr:title>EDGE: Explorer of diffuse emission and gamma-ray burst explosions</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Experimental Astronomy</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.ukri.org:80/person/911d3204dd22c3562dc9b25c16c10b7c"><gtr:id>911d3204dd22c3562dc9b25c16c10b7c</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Piro L</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2008-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:outcomeId>bib_17438_0f9584969b</gtr:outcomeId></gtr:publication><gtr:publication><gtr:id>70243BA9-E966-43D5-AA58-DCD9EFF2057C</gtr:id><gtr:title>The performance of thin shell adaptive optics for high angular resolution x-ray telescopes</gtr:title><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.ukri.org:80/person/90b7eb5260ec3539a9c7d7bf75d025d1"><gtr:id>